reviewDescription: I feel Himalaya Neem Face Wash is an amazing affordable daily face wash for ladies with oily to combination skin. It is excellent at cleansing the skin and fighting those tiny breakouts and bumps. However, I suggest using this only once a day. When I use it more than once a day, it kind of dries out my skin. In fact, this face wash doubles up as a body wash as well in case you want to travel light and do not have space to carry a separate body wash and face wash. Lastly, please do not forget to share your experiences with this product in the comments below.
